Mobile Roadside Repair serving Delmarva & sorrounding areas. For your convenience our knowledgeable mechanics arrive at your breakdown location in a fully equipped service truck. Authorized to service the local weigh stations. Certified & capable of completing required violation paperwork when put OOS for mandated repairs. JDE specializes in tractor & trailer, box trucks, car carriers etc.. Offering mobile roadside service for a wide range of breakdowns. From a clutch replacement to a simple lock-out or the possibility of no fuel. Never is a call too much to assess, nor too small to bother. Quite the opposite, having 17yrs as an owner-operator, we are the few left that not only relate but care about the safety & operation of your truck."
